12:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":["$","em",null,{"children":"Indirect emissions"}]}]," - Emissions from your operations' purchased electricity, steam, and heating/cooling; Emissions from sources that your company does not own or control, such as supplier emissions, business travel, and end-of-life emissions from sold products."]}]
13:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":["We, at WIZMS one of the best"," ",["$","$Lf",null,{"href":"/","className":"text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800","children":"ISO certification consultant in UAE"}]," ","develop the scope based on the company's needs and the location where majority of the emissions takes place. Our ISO consultants in UAE, Dubai focus on confirming your annual GHG emissions and start the verification process. The verification is carried out in accordance with ISO 14064-1, which is a guideline for verifiers on how to verify emissions. At last, our ISO 14064 certification consultants in Dubai will give you a verification statement. This statement gives an assurance to your stakeholders and investors about the accuracy of your carbon footprint claims. Our carbon footprint verification services in Dubai and rest of UAE have also received external recognition from types of organizations."]}]
14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Advantages of ISO 14064 Certification in Dubai, UAE"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-2","children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Integrity"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":"ISO 14064-1 certification in Dubai demonstrates the authenticity of your systems and processes by proving your GHG inventory, assertions, and reports that fit to the ISO 14064 standard and are free of errors, omissions, or misstatements."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-2","children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Targets"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":"ISO 14064-1 certification ensures the integrity of your project baseline, design plan, and supporting assumptions, guaranteed that your projected GHG emissions are reduced."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-2","children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Success"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":"ISO 14064-1 carbon footprint verification provides the necessary assurance. Our ISO consultants will validate your GHG projects to ISO 14064-1 certification and provides assurance that it is implemented as planned and assist them to achieve projected emission reductions. ISO 14064-1 carbon footprint verification assures your stakeholders that GHG emission reductions are attained."}]]}]
15:["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10 bg-lime-50 border-l-4 border-lime-500 p-6 rounded","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":"WIZMS was the first verification bodies in Dubai, UAE to achieve accreditation to ISO 14064. We deliver carbon footprint verification to ISO 14064-1 to any type of organization and in any business sector. Our ISO 14064-1 carbon footprint verification services are designed to develop robust, and reproducible strategies to monitor & report GHG emissions, both at project and organization level."}]}]
